OL,4,G1925FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAt Chris's glampsite in Richmond,
OL,6,     GNorth Yorkshire, off-grid really
OL,7,     Gdoes mean off the electricity
OL,8,     Ggrid. Which is quite a worry for
OL,9,     Gsome of the B&Bers...
OL,10,G1955FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GFor the final visit the B&Bers go
OL,12,     Gglamping again, at Phil and
OL,13,     GJane's site in Derbyshire, where
OL,14,     Gthe stag-gering views include
OL,15,     Greal-life deer wandering about
OL,16,     Gthe place.
OL,17,G2025FFour in a Bed
OL,18,     GOn payment day, the B&Bers clash
OL,19,     Gover furniture failings and clock
OL,20,     Gcomplaints. And sparks fly -
OL,21,     Gironically - over a lack of
OL,22,     Gelectricity. Who's won?
